<div class='d-flex justify-content-end mb-3'>
    <%= link_to "https://vertiflor.co.id/", 
                target: "_blank", 
                rel: "noopener noreferrer", 
                class: 'c-btn align-right', 
                aria: { label: "Visit Vertiflor website" } do %>
        <span class="c-btn__label">Visit vertiflor.co.id →</span>
    <% end %>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <%= image_tag 'vertiflor-main-photo.webp', 
                  alt: "Vertiflor main appearance", 
                  width: "1200", height: "675", 
                  loading: "eager", 
                  class: "img-fluid" %>
</div>

<div class="row my-2 g-5">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <%= image_tag 'vertiflor-2.webp', 
                      alt: "Vertiflor mobile view", 
                      width: "600", height: "800", 
                      loading: "lazy", 
                      class: "img-fluid" %>

        <div class="my-5 px-2">
            <h3>Challenges & Solutions</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Client Requirement for WordPress</strong> – Worked within platform limitations while ensuring a custom, high-end look.</li>
                <li><strong>Balancing Design & Performance</strong> – Maintained a visually rich experience without compromising speed.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="my-5 px-2">
            <h3>Responsibilities</h3>
            <p><strong>UX Design</strong> – Developed a magazine editorial-style layout to enhance the brand’s premium aesthetic.</p>
            <p><strong>Development</strong> – Built the website using WordPress while mentoring a junior developer throughout the process.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <div class='mb-5 px-2'>
            <h3>Overview</h3>
            <p>
                Vertiflor is a luxury vinyl flooring brand. The project involved designing and developing a website that effectively showcases the brand’s products, values, and services while ensuring a smooth user experience.
            </p>
        </div>

        <%= image_tag 'vertiflor-3.webp', 
                      alt: "Vertiflor shop tablet view", 
                      width: "800", height: "600", 
                      loading: "lazy", 
                      class: "img-fluid" %>

        <div class="p-3 row d-flex justify-content-start align-items-center my-5">
            <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-4">
                <div class="horizontal-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-8 pt-3">
                <p>Visit the Vertiflor website to see the project live:</p>
                <%= link_to "https://vertiflor.co.id/", 
                            target: "_blank", 
                            rel: "noopener noreferrer", 
                            class: 'c-btn align-right', 
                            aria: { label: "Visit Vertiflor website" } do %>
                    <span class="c-btn__label">Visit vertiflor.co.id →</span>
                <% end %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
